<title>ḥnạnk yạrb ạlạ̉kwạn</title>
<lyrics>[C1]
   ạlqrạr: ḥnạnk yạ rb̃ ạlạ̉kwạn ạ̹lyk rfʿt ṣlạty
   ạ̉nạ ạ̹n ạ̉ḥyạ fbạlạ̹ymạn ysẖr̃f mʿny̱ ḥyạty

[V1]
 1- smʿt ndạʾk yạ rb̃y yjljl fy ạ̉ʿmạqy
 ṣdaⁿy̱ ytjạwb fy qlby mʿ ạlngẖm ạlkẖf̃ạq
 fsrt bhdyka fy drby wby ẓmạ̉ ạlmsẖtạq
 lmnhlk ạlṣạfy ạlʿdẖb ạ̉rw̃y bh ạ̉mnyạty

[V2]
 2- yrw̃ʿny ṣkẖb ạlbḥr wṣwt qṣyf ạlrʿwd
 fậns mnk mʿ ạlfjr bfyḍ ạlrḍy̱ wạljwd
 fyạ mbdʿ ạlkwn mn ydry swạk bsr̃ ạlwjwd
 fkm fyk yạ rb̃ mn sriⁿ̃ wậyạtiⁿ mdẖhlạti

[V3]
 3- ạ̹lhy ạ̹n ạ̉dʿw fmạ ly swạk mjybu ndạỷy
 wḥyn ạ̉nwʾ bạ̉tẖqạly fly brḍạk ʿzạỷy
 ṭrḥt mnạy wậmạly ldyk wkl̃ rjạỷy
 fạ̉nt mlạdẖy wmậly ạ̹lyk wfyk njạty</lyrics>
</song>